Read all HMMs in a directory into a list

Source: R/io-methods.R
multi_read_hmm.Rd

Read all HMMs in a directory into a list

Usage

multi_read_hmm(directory)

Arguments

directory

Path to a directory containing profile HMMs (*.hmm)

Value

A base::list() of HMMs.

Examples

hmms <- multi_read_hmm(padlocdev_example("hmm"))
hmms[1]
